mesalazine. The average costs per QALY for OD and BD mesalazine were €5433 and 
€6324 for OD and BD, respectively.
CONCLUSIONS: Based on the results from a single randomized study, OD dosing 
resulted in a shorter time spent in active UC which resulted in lower healthcare 
costs.

