Discrepancies in the estimates of life expectancy after SCI.

Shavelle R(1), Strauss D, Brooks J.

Author information:
(1)Life Expectancy Project, San Francisco, CA, USA.

Comment in
    Spinal Cord. 2013 Dec;51(12):938-9.

